{"tid":571680,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美女吸冰毒後幻聽　為「上天堂」教堂外自挖雙目","createTime":"2018-02-25T01:28:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-25T03:30:55.000Z","uid":53379,"like":2,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"dd6598c031318abc91fc4c2e0e8734fadbfa0546","tid":571680,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T01:28:43.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">美國女吸冰毒後幻聽　為「上天堂」教堂外自挖雙目</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180224/s00005/c5ffd20fc46e47a648fd0121e4153846.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180224%2Fs00005%2Fc5ffd20fc46e47a648fd0121e4153846.jpg&h=5693d7fa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國一名20歲女子，吸食冰毒後出現幻聽，竟在教堂外自挖雙目「奉獻」以「上天堂」。其家人發起網上籌款，希望領養導盲犬，助她出院後繼續生活。<br />\n<br />\n事發在美國南卡羅萊納州一間教堂，信眾本月6日聽到20歲的穆法特（Kaylee Muthart）在教堂外尖叫，出外查看時，赫見她正手持一個眼球。穆法特更掙脫嘗試制服她的信眾和途人，結果至救護人員趕到時，她已將另一個眼球也挖了出來。<br />\n<br />\n穆法特將永久失明，她由直升機送院後，醫生為她清理留在眼眶的組織等，防止日後出現感染。醫生相信，她吸食的冰毒中，混有另一種代學物質，令她出現幻聽，聽到聲音叫她「奉獻雙眼」，以令自己上天堂。<br />\n<br />\n穆法特母親湯普金斯（Katy Tompkins）指，女兒是誤服冰毒，稱她是吸食朋友提供的大麻，不料當中混有冰毒。湯普金斯又說，事發前一天是其生日，她原本打算當日送女兒到戒毒中心，「但我太遲了」。<br />\n<br />\n仍然留醫的穆法特正在康復中，其家人在網上籌款，希望籌得1.2萬美元（近9.4萬港元）領養導盲犬，協助她出院後的生活，至今獲近8300美元（近6.5萬港元）捐款。<br />\n<br />\n（太陽報）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180224/s00005/1519462197090\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180224%2Fs00005%2F1519462197090&d=DVWoahwgonv%2FIpZBhWpyB9tKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=a1968186\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180224%2Fs00005%2F1519462197090&h=edf78bf3\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180224/s00005/1519462197090</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e4ea1260b67408a5a497c2b912fd4c92c426d94","tid":571680,"uid":51932,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T01:36:47.000Z","msg":"自作孽，仲想人埋單俾錢佢洗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52d7a5d5fea6c05eb74b396c422e2ac222871be0","tid":571680,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T01:38:03.000Z","msg":"協助她出院後的生活，至今獲近8300美元"},{"pid":"7607eb99f0d45ed5b8fc4557873041260c1cbd9a","tid":571680,"uid":91664,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T01:47:42.000Z","msg":"屌得過"},{"pid":"611cbfbc85bc26b838208b2d4d7a9abcb258ea33","tid":571680,"uid":87778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T01:49:39.000Z","msg":"大把黑人排隊收養。btw毒品不可一不可再<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff40ee1420509fe4af24315536bd1aece8dada0e","tid":571680,"uid":64345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T02:02:58.000Z","msg":"耶撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53883a28ddf2abe26b15906f312749fa9d3fe095","tid":571680,"uid":120070,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T02:12:01.000Z","msg":"好high唷"},{"pid":"175c20fdc5180ade64f54d268d7b50dbe5af3cd7","tid":571680,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T02:14:41.000Z","msg":"屌盲妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ade4e28bf4e47aa72f9a19d9145966757199b9d0","tid":571680,"uid":71257,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T02:50:35.000Z","msg":"死廢青 出黎做雞/拍av啦"},{"pid":"a5ab8e9a2a532adcc00411d5e75c78f414994c78","tid":571680,"uid":132302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-25T03:30:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}